text: Blaine Chad Woodson (born October 30, 1995) is an American professional Canadian football defensive lineman who is currently a free agent. He was signed by the San Francisco 49ers of the National Football League (NFL) as an undrafted free agent in 2018 after playing college football for Delaware.
